To build this package, use cmake.

Requirements:
fftw3 must be installed (version 3.10 likely needed)
c++17 compiler (if not available by default, set using CC and CXX)

from this directory do:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -D CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<insert prefix here> -D CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=<path2fftw3> ../
make
make install

